text:
Photo: Michael Short, Special To The Chronicle Mayor Ed Lee gets a look at the interior of a new Muni bus during a news conference announcing service improvements in San Francisco on Sept. 28, 2015. Mayor Ed Lee gets a look at the interior of a new Muni bus during a...
When the Board of Supervisors appointed Ed Lee the city’s interim mayor in January 2011, they characterized him as a caretaker who would diligently keep city government chugging along until voters picked their real leader.
